codex
The endpoint now captures the JSON parser’s raw bytes, validates a lower-case HMAC safely, enforces the event shape, and records accepted IDs only after validation. I also added focused coverage for acceptance, replay, stale-signature tampering, and valid-signature invalid bodies.
