codex
I found one contract conflict during the final requirement reread: the plan ordered full body validation before deduplication, while the generated spec requires a repeated accepted ID to return `409` regardless of the second body. The spec is controlling, so I’m moving the duplicate check immediately after signature verification and adding that exact regression case.
